            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potato has softened, mash with a fork</p><p>Add the <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>crab meat </strong>to the mashed potato with<strong> half </strong>the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped shallot </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>crab filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
