      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust a work surface with a small handful of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap the <strong>puff pastry </strong>and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Cut into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> rectangles and add them to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 4,
